How did your memories come back? My father was VERY abusive with me ever since I can remember. During my childhood, adolescence and youth he insulted me everyday, yelled at me, made fun of me, told me things that were really projections of himself. I'm an adult now and he's the same. He doesn't have any friends, nobody likes him and he treats my mom very badly. I have a blurry memory from then I was 3 years old, about a sexual abuse from him. He touched me and put me over his penis but no penetration. He's a doctor so he knew he couldn't do anything that left evidence. It was a suppressed memory that came back when I moved out of the house. My family doesn't believe me, specially my brother. I'm a woman and my father hates women. My father is very violent and manipulative and it's hard to know for sure if that really happened.
